# TODO(brand): Drop Geist woff2 files here to activate the brand typography.
# Download from https://github.com/vercel/geist-font/releases (assets: Geist.zip)
# Required files:
#   Geist-Regular.woff2   (weight 400)
#   Geist-Medium.woff2    (weight 500)
#   Geist-SemiBold.woff2  (weight 600)
# Then uncomment the @font-face block in frontend/src/styles/theme.css.
# The system-font fallback stack is identical, so nothing breaks before drop-in.
